南美南方共同市场集团的贸易协议谈判中找到友好解决方案，并且正在与所有合作伙伴进行谈判，其中包括反对该协议的法国。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 12:11:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/germany-says-amicable-solution-remains-goal-mercosur-deal-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：长期债券收益率在就业数据公布前回落，法国反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-06/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:05:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>立陶宛认为波罗的海电缆“很有可能”被故意切断</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/quite-high-probability-that-baltic-sea-cables-were-cut-intentionally-lithuania-2024-12-06/</link><description>立陶宛总统吉塔纳斯·瑙塞达周五表示，上个月在波罗的海受损的两条海底光缆很可能是故意切断的。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 10:45:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/quite-high-probability-that-baltic-sea-cables-were-cut-intentionally-lithuania-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>西方国家对中国感到不安，忙于重组关键矿产供应链</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rattled-by-china-west-scrambles-rejig-critical-minerals-supply-chains-2024-12-06/</link><description>中国对战略矿产的贸易限制开始打击西方公司的痛处。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 10:40:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rattled-by-china-west-scrambles-rejig-critical-minerals-supply-chains-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院驳回活动人士根据新国安法提早获释的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-rejects-activists-bid-early-release-under-new-security-law-2024-12-06/</link><description>香港一家法院周五驳回了一名根据中国实施的国安法因分裂国家罪被监禁的活动人士提出的提早出狱的上诉。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 10:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-rejects-activists-bid-early-release-under-new-security-law-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金印度经销商提供折扣；中国需求季节性疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-indian-dealers-offer-discounts-china-sees-seasonally-soft-demand-2024-12-06/</link><description>印度的实物黄金六周来首次打折出售，因为卢比疲软推高了价格，进而抑制了需求，而最大消费国中国的需求出现季节性放缓。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 08:13:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-indian-dealers-offer-discounts-china-sees-seasonally-soft-demand-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>NBA将重返中国 与澳门签订多年合约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/nba-inks-multi-year-deal-with-macau-casino-sands-china-play-gambling-hub-2024-12-06/</link><description>美国国家篮球协会(NBA)签署了一份多年期协议，从2025年起在澳门举行季前赛，这标志着该联盟在2019年香港抗议活动引发争议后阔别中国市场多年后重返中国市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 06:52:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/basketball/nba-inks-multi-year-deal-with-macau-casino-sands-china-play-gambling-hub-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>越南对美国贸易顺差飙升引发对特朗普关税的新担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-soaring-us-trade-surplus-stokes-new-fears-trump-tariffs-2024-12-06/</link><description>行业高管和分析师表示，由于数据显示越南对美国的贸易顺差不断膨胀，越南很容易成为特朗普新政府的下一个关税目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 06:34:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-soaring-us-trade-surplus-stokes-new-fears-trump-tariffs-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：风险警惕的市场倒计时就业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-06/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 05:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>报道：中国将举办2019年以来首场NBA季前赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/reports-china-set-host-first-nba-preseason-games-since-2019-2024-12-06/</link><description>据周四的多份报道称，NBA 与中国的关系在 2019 年因总经理的一条推文而变得冷淡，但随着周五宣布将于 10 月在澳门举行两场季前赛，NBA 与中国的关系显然正在解冻。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 05:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/reports-china-set-host-first-nba-preseason-games-since-2019-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>在预期的战争游戏之前，台湾敦促中国“松开拳头”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ahead-expected-war-games-taiwan-urges-china-unclench-its-fists-2024-12-06/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周五敦促中国“松开拳头”，不要采取任何单方面行动，并在预计中国将在台湾举行军演之前表示，北京不会通过军事演习赢得任何尊重。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 03:56:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ahead-expected-war-games-taiwan-urges-china-unclench-its-fists-2024-12-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾在南海对峙后与盟友举行演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/united-states-japan-philippine-conduct-maritime-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-12-06/</link><description>菲律宾军方周五表示，菲律宾与美国和日本在南海专属经济区内举行海上演习，两天前，菲律宾与北京围绕争议浅滩发生海上对峙。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 02:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/united-states-japan-philippine-conduct-maritime-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-12-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>